，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》&quot;"},{"pid":"2c70b38979db987825c39d41d30236fc3d3e9198","tid":1961280,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T15:23:58.000Z","msg":"聽番花花首。<br />\n好想愛這個世界啊囉"}]}